# Repo-local skills

Per-repo Codex skills for `<!-- PARAMETERIZE: project_name -->`. Skills are execution guardrails for specific recurring tasks. Not sources of truth. If a skill conflicts with a canonical doc (`AGENTS.md`, `docs/PRD.md`, `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md`, or a canonical workflow doc), the canonical doc wins.

