## Skill rules

- Prefer explicit invocation for high-stakes work, for example: "use docs-sync skill" or "use implementation-guardrails skill."
- Do not invent additional repo skills unless explicitly requested.
- Skills are guardrails, not capabilities. They constrain how a task is performed; they do not unlock new things to do.

